summary: An Ordinance transferring the sum of One Hundred Fifty-five and 07/100 Dollars ($155.07) from Local Improvement District No. 1856 Fund, into the General Fund of the City of Seattle, for the purpose of reimbursing said General Fund, for the deficiency in the fixed estimate of said district, for the improvement Warren Avenue, and Second Avenue North, under Ordinance No. 19249.
